public class MethodWithArgs
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.dmd.dmc.DmcMappedAttributeIF, java.io.Serializable

The MethodWithArgs class is used to store a local method call and possibly an argument vector and fully qualified class names in the form: returnType functionName(type arg1, type arg2...) comment...
